name: Eno Bening In A Boomers Vacation
name_original: Eno Bening In A Boomers Vacation
description:
Play as Eno Bening, as you trapped in a cave.

CAN YOU SURVIVE THE MADNESS IN THIS CAVE??

This game was made in 1 weeks, when I'm still on school doing exams.

*Gamenya gratis, kalian tinggal click " No thanks, just take me to the downloads"

Kalau pingin donasi silahkan, tapi gua gatau mau diapain uangnya. Charity mungkin?

Bila game di block AntiVirus, kalian bisa matikan AntiVirusnya sebentar, kebanyakan Antivirus mendeteksi Game buatan Unity sebagai Virus, tapi nyatanya tidak, itu cuma False positive, jadi tidak berpengaruh!.
